{
  "total_duration": 527.076,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 11.52,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象老师很严肃地说：“下课后来我办公室一下。”你一路走过去，心里可能已经开始排队猜坏结果：是不是作业出问题了？是不是要被批评？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 11.87,
      "end": 28.486,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Good news"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“佳音”。这篇课文不是单纯讲办公室，而是讲一种心理反转：权威人物叫你进去，语气很严肃，每一个线索都像坏消息，最后却变成好消息。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 28.836,
      "end": 44.183,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把旧办公室背景说清楚。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "secretary"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是帮老板安排见面、传话的办公室工作人员。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mr. Harmsworth would see me"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“看见我一眼”，而是老板要和我谈话。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 44.533,
      "end": 63.309,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "firm"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 company，公司。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "salary"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是工作以后定期拿到的工资。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "business was very bad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是公司情况不好。如果公司付不起工资，又已经有人离开，员工当然会担心：是不是轮到我倒霉了？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 63.659,
      "end": 79.514,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以听这一课时，先别急着看结尾。你要跟着作者一起紧张：老板不抬头，生意很糟，工资太高，二十个人已经走了。等到最后一句，题目"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Good news"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "才真正亮起来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 79.864,
      "end": 94.288,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，消息来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The secretary told me that Mr. Harmsworth would see me."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "秘书通知作者，老板要见他。这个开头本身不一定坏，但它像“下课后来一下”一样，会让人开始胡思乱想。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 94.638,
      "end": 112.174,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，作者进了办公室："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I felt very nervous when I went into his office."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他非常紧张。更糟的是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He did not look up from his desk when I entered."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老板连头也没抬。这个安静的动作，让气氛更像坏消息。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 112.524,
      "end": 129.331,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，老板终于开口，但内容听起来更危险："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After I had sat down, he said that business was very bad."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着他又说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the firm could not afford to pay such large salaries."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "公司付不起这么高的工资。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 129.681,
      "end": 149.441,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后还有一句："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Twenty people had already left."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "二十个人已经离开了。作者听到这里，心里几乎已经下结论："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I knew that my turn had come."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "my turn had come"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是轮到我玩游戏，而是“这下该轮到我倒霉了”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 149.79,
      "end": 165.254,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，作者想开口，声音都弱了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"Mr. Harmsworth,\" I said in a weak voice."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "weak voice"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是没有底气的声音。老板却说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "\"Don't interrupt,\" he said."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "别打断我。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 165.604,
      "end": 183.052,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一下好像更紧张了。可是下一秒，老板笑了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Then he smiled and told me I would receive an extra thousand pounds a year!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "原来不是裁掉他，而是给他每年多一千英镑。前面所有坏消息的线索，突然变成了反转铺垫。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 183.402,
      "end": 188.777,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文为什么叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Good news"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，而不是一开始就让人开心？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 189.127,
      "end": 198.937,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为前面听起来全是坏消息。老板要见他，老板不抬头，生意不好，公司付不起工资，还有二十个人已经离开。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 199.287,
      "end": 207.407,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。作者的紧张不是凭空来的。他把每个线索都听成一个方向：公司不好，别人走了，我可能也要走。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 207.757,
      "end": 211.964,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "my turn had come"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是什么意思？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 212.314,
      "end": 223.354,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "字面是“轮到我了”。但在这里不是开心地轮到我，而是作者以为“坏事轮到我了”。中文可以理解成：完了，这次该到我了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 223.704,
      "end": 229.201,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老板说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Don't interrupt"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，是不是也让误会更深？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 229.551,
      "end": 240.671,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是的。作者想解释或求情，老板一句话把他停住，悬念又拉高了一点。直到老板 smiles，才说明事情不是他想的那样。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 241.021,
      "end": 243.327,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以 good news 为什么更好？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 243.677,
      "end": 257.157,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它来得晚。前面越像坏消息，最后的好消息就越让人松一口气。标题的笑点也在这里：你以为要听坏消息，结果听到的是升工资。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 257.507,
      "end": 261.563,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The secretary told me that Mr. Harmsworth would see me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
