        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 347.26,
      "end": 360.292,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "interrupt"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "interrupt"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是打断别人说话。作者刚想开口，老板说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Don't interrupt."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话短、硬、很有压力，也让作者更以为坏消息要来了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 360.642,
      "end": 370.362,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 是 reported speech，也就是转述别人说过的话。先别做机械变形，我们先看故事为什么需要它。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 370.711,
      "end": 384.723,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文像作者事后在复述一次办公室谈话。他不是一直用引号直播，而是用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "told me that"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "said that"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "把别人说过的话讲给我们听。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 385.073,
      "end": 395.793,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "秘书说的话变成："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The secretary told me that Mr. Harmsworth would see me."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老板说的话变成："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He said that business was very bad."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 396.143,
      "end": 410.134,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老板继续说的话变成："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He told me that the firm could not afford to pay such large salaries."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后的好消息也用转述："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He told me I would receive an extra thousand pounds a year."
        }
      ]
