    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 438.369,
      "end": 455.929,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的“以为是坏消息，结果是好消息”放进你自己的生活。下面三个场景都要填，word bank 里选短语。可以写老师、家长、教练、社团负责人，重点是轻松的小误会，不要写很痛苦的惩罚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 456.279,
      "end": 482.779,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "关键句型是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I felt very nervous when ___ . I thought ___ . Then ___ smiled and told me ___ ."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比如："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I felt very nervous when my teacher asked me to stay after class. I thought I was in trouble. Then she smiled and told me I had done very well."
        }
      ]
    },
